$$\frac{52}{3} = \frac{1}{3}h(S_{ABC} + \sqrt{S_{ABC}S_{A_1B_1C_1}} + S_{A_1B_1C_1}) = \frac{1}{3}h(9\sqrt{3} + 3\sqrt{3} + \sqrt{3}) = \frac{13\sqrt{3}}{3}h$$

