Finally, in right triangle $O_1AO$, we have 
$$\tan \angle O_1AO = \frac{OO_1}{O_1A} = \frac{h}{OA - O_1A_1} = \frac{4}{2\sqrt{3} - \frac{2\sqrt{3}}{3}} = \boxed{3}$$

