因为 $AB = 6$，所以 $BD = DC = 3$.

因为 $A_1B_1 = 2$，所以 $S_{\triangle A_1B_1C_1} = \frac{\sqrt{3}}{4} \cdot 2^2 = \sqrt{3}$.

由三棱台的体积公式可知，$\frac{1}{3} \cdot \frac{52}{3} = \frac{1}{3} \cdot \sqrt{3} \cdot A_1O$，解得 $A_1O = \frac{52}{3\sqrt{3}}$.

在 $\triangle AOD$ 中，$AD = \frac{\sqrt{3}}{2} \cdot AB = 3\sqrt{3}$，所以 $\tan \angle A_1AO = \frac{A_1O}{AO} = \frac{A_1O}{\sqrt{AD^2 - OD^2}} = \frac{52}{3\sqrt{3}} \div \sqrt{27 - \frac{9}{4}} = 2$.

